  "texts": [
    "More specifically, the correlated regime holds for masses lower than m φ ∼ 2 × 10 -24 eV; the pulsar correlated regime for 2 × 10 -24 eV m φ 5 × 10 -23 eV and the uncorrelated limit for m φ 5 × 10 -23 eV.",
    "We defer a more detailed study to future analysis.",
    "Based on the above, we fit the model from Eq.",
    "(31) to the DR2new as in Smarra et al. (2023).",
    "As an example, marginalised posterior distributions for Ψ c and m φ are plotted in Fig. 21."
